Many university students struggle to manage coursework, track academic progress, maintain study consistency, and identify areas requiring improvement. Existing learning systems often provide course access but lack intelligent insights that help students improve performance.

The proposed AI-Powered Student Success Platform, named Lumen, addresses these challenges by combining learning management features with AI-driven progress tracking, performance analytics, personalized recommendations, and student engagement tools. The platform enables students to monitor learning progress, manage assignments, maintain study streaks, and receive data-driven insights to improve academic outcomes.
